### Credit Note API Tests

# Note: Replace {{baseUrl}}, {{token}}, {{companyId}}, {{clientId}}, and {{invoiceId}} with actual values

@baseUrl = http://localhost:9000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE
@companyId = YOUR_COMPANY_ID_HERE

@invoiceId = YOUR_INVOICE_ID_HERE

@clientId = YOUR_CREDIT_NOTE_ID_HERE

@creditNoteId = YOUR_CREDIT_NOTE_ID_HERE

### 1. Create Credit Note
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "invoiceId": "{{invoiceId}}",
  "creditNoteNumber": "CN-001",
  "creditNoteDate": "2025-01-15",
  "originalInvoiceNumber": "INV-001",
  "originalInvoiceDate": "2025-01-01",
  "taxType": "exclusive",
  "discountType": "flat",
  "discountValue": 0,
  "shipping": 0,
  "roundOff": false,
  "showHSN": true,
  "showUnit": true,
  "showSignature": false,
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Product A",
      "hsn": "1234",
      "unit": "pcs",
      "quantity": 2,
      "rate": 100,
      "discount": 0,
      "discountType": "flat",
      "taxType": "cgst_sgst",
      "taxRate": 18,
      "reason": "Quality issue with the product"
    }
  ],
  "reason": "Customer complained about product quality",
  "creditType": "quality_issue",
  "terms": "Credit note terms and conditions",
  "notes": "Additional notes for this credit note",
  "priority": "high"
}

### 2. Get All Credit Notes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Credit Notes with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes?page=1&limit=10&status=draft&priority=high&startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31&search=CN-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Credit Note by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Update Credit Note
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Updated reason for credit note",
  "priority": "medium",
  "notes": "Updated notes"
}

### 6. Approve Credit Note
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approvalNotes": "Approved after review"
}

### 7. Update Credit Note Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "acknowledged",
  "notes": "Client has acknowledged the credit note"
}

### 8. Mark Credit Note as Resolved
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resolutionStatus": "refund_processed",
  "resolutionNotes": "Refund has been processed to client account",
  "adjustmentAmount": 236
}

### 9. Dispute Credit Note
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}/dispute
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Client disputes the credit note amount"
}

### 10. Get Credit Note Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Credit Notes by Invoice
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/invoice/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Credit Notes by Client
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Delete Credit Note (only draft status)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/finance/sales/credit-notes/{{creditNoteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

